                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote scope="major" script="naskh">
                        <desc>Written in informal Egyptian Naskh by two hands. The first part was written by<persName xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied">Ḥusayn ibn Naṣṣār ibn Manṣūr al-Ḥanbalī al-Maqdisī<foreign xml:lang="ar">حسين ابن نصار ابن منصور الحنبلي المقدسي</foreign>
                           </persName>who finished it on<date calendar="#Hijri-qamari" when="1741">Saturday 10th Ṣafar 1154</date>. The second part of the manuscript was finished on<date calendar="#Hijri-qamari" when="1744">Monday Jumādā I</date>in the<placeName xml:lang="en">Al-Azhar Mosque</placeName>.</desc>
